description: Yes, Jimmy Rowles -- the pianist, the man, and the artist, with side-glances at Robert Mitchum, Henry Mancini, and The Fifth Dimension, Tommy Flanagan, Phyllis Diller, Benny Carter, Michael's own recording with Rowles, Ray Brown, and some comments on race.  Recorded by Michael Steinman for JAZZ LIVES (http://www.jazzlives.wordpress.com).
